        <aside>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>FAQ bot</h4>
            <p class="small muted">Ask short questions. The bot uses simple rules to reply. If it can't, it will save your question for manual reply.</p>
            <div class="bot" id="botAnswer">Bot is ready ‚Äî ask something or click "Ask the Bot".</div>
